{"tid":1359753,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我們還未失去任何東西","createTime":"2019-07-24T08:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:19:19.000Z","uid":262187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b20a5f5b36f5a81cb657cb83b432623570ef48","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"革命一日未完, <br />\n就算踩住兄弟既屍體都要向前行,<br />\n行上前線既兄弟,<br />\n都係為左同樣既目標而奮戰,<br />\n離開左既兄弟, 即使失去左生命,<br />\n但佢地既目標一樣好明確,<br />\n佢既意志會留係我地心入面,<br />\n只要我地一日未放棄,<br />\n我地就無失去到任何野!<br />\n<br />\n大家都為了這場革命, 拼上了一切<br />\n我還, 還未失去任何東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n官 商 鄉 黑 警, 我地一個都唔會放過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x86A72o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx86A72o.png&h=c39eb93e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCvimnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCvimnr.png&h=a8e0ca97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac48e1cdc68f803065c91d5e3e7883e19bf67315","tid":1359753,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"不要停下來啊～！！！"},{"pid":"3943b231143f6180b67be398e57f1f9139eab693","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"前路幾難行都好, 總有翻盤既機會,<br />\n只有放棄既時候, 先係真正失去,<br />\n各位兄弟, 堅持到底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivTG3Cq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivTG3Cq.png&h=d496951e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKkus39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKkus39.png&h=4672c764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d6fdd84659c0cabc04fe971f69c6dd4c1bba3ac","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AQToxxY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQToxxY.png&h=38540b74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cGZ3xxW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcGZ3xxW.png&h=8ea340c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqPZQjy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqPZQjy.png&h=2fc019d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾張圖, 我唔識點形容...<br />\n只係想睇到既人明白, <br />\n我地只要肯企出黎,<br />\n無任何力量可以阻擋到我地,<br />\n群眾所組成既政府, <br />\n無群眾既支持/默許,<br />\n只會步向滅亡"},{"pid":"398cb49246c4924075261eee705bc66d9838ab3b","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtWp1uj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtWp1uj.png&h=0df09879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSzCB2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSzCB2W.png&h=518200c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KpozEgu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKpozEgu.png&h=7e3c4a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場一致, 為對方背負不必要既伽鎖,<br />\n可以死, 但唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄, 放棄既當下,<br />\n就勝負已分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伽羅bb你死得好撚慘"},{"pid":"d92811016efc96ae1f3f414103ff4810703e3073","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d26769988d61f5a2ce8212638c6c5a11b223f","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MetvW6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMetvW6B.png&h=913c91e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JO0zTj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JO0zTj.png&h=e144d53a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BkANZkj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBkANZkj.png&h=7f1d969a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟既離開, 唔係要我地灰心,<br />\n我地要做既係變得更強大,<br />\n傷心難免, 但喊過之後企返起身,<br />\n我 地 仲 未 輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef32a839edba01f0967e31b3a65dcbda1fdf8c5","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31ba419664baea3d86c00e60f47650873f829c5","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07f0783c2f937cc0d2a35bce30b515d17a3084f","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4da2974ca9cec0d3c105dfd209cf79ef81a5f0e","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d548b5a986c9cd87d44e5fef4eff264082cc4b2","tid":1359753,"uid":262187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQ3zEpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd